---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - Mobazha" description="Mobazha Terms of Service. Read our terms for using the platform.">
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-32 pb-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">Last updated: April 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-8 text-[var(--color-text-body)] leading-relaxed">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            By accessing or using the Mobazha platform ("Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, do not use the Service.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">2. Description of Service</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Mobazha provides a decentralized commerce platform that enables users to create online stores, list products, and accept payments through cryptocurrency and traditional payment methods. The Service is available as a hosted SaaS solution and as self-hosted software.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">3. User Accounts</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            You are responsible for maintaining the security of your account credentials. You must not share your password or grant access to your account to any third party. You are responsible for all activities that occur under your account.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">4. Prohibited Uses</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">You agree not to use the Service to:</p>
          <ul class="mt-2 ml-6 list-disc space-y-1">
            <li>Sell illegal goods or services in your jurisdiction</li>
            <li>Engage in fraud, money laundering, or terrorist financing</li>
            <li>Violate any applicable laws or regulations</li>
            <li>Infringe on the intellectual property rights of others</li>
            <li>Distribute malware or engage in any form of cyberattack</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">5. Payments and Fees</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Mobazha charges zero commissions on sales. During the Beta period, all features are free. When paid plans are introduced, pricing changes will be communicated at least 30 days in advance. Third-party payment processors (Stripe, PayPal) may charge their own fees.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">6. Buyer Protection and Escrow</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            Cryptocurrency payments may be secured through smart contract escrow. Escrow provides automatic payment protection, but Mobazha does not guarantee the outcome of any transaction or dispute between buyers and sellers.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">7. Data Ownership</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            You retain ownership of all data you create on the platform. You may export your data at any time. For self-hosted deployments, all data resides entirely on your own infrastructure.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            The Service is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. Mobazha shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of the Service, including but not limited to loss of funds from cryptocurrency transactions.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">9. Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            We may update these Terms from time to time. Material changes will be communicated via the platform or email. Continued use of the Service after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-primary)]">10. Contact</h2>
          <p class="mt-3">
            For questions about these Terms, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@mobazha.org" class="text-[var(--color-brand-light)] hover:underline">hello@mobazha.org</a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
